<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>EH3</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
<style>
 body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin:0;
background:#fafafa;
color:#333;
}

header{
background:#130;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
}

nav{
background:#eee;
text-align:center;
padding:15px;
}

nav a{
margin:15px;
text-decoration:none;
color:#333;
font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:80px 20px;
background:#f5f5f5;
}

section{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px;
}

.button{
background:#000;
color:white;
padding:12px 20px;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:5px;
}

.book{
background:white;
padding:20px;
margin-bottom:25px;
border-radius:6px;
box-shadow:0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
background:#130;
color:white;
margin-top:50px;
}   

.button:hover, .button:active, .button:focus { 
                background-color: rgb(56, 107, 66);
                 
            }  
 
 nav a:hover, nav a:active, nav a:focus {
            color: rgb(56, 107, 66);
        } 
    
</style>
    
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Poetry</h1>
</header>

<section>

<h2>Morning Prayer</h2>

<p>

Lord guide my steps today<br>
Through valleys deep and wide<br>
Let faith be my compass<br>
And love be my guide

</p>

</section>

</body>
</html>
